name: Synder Anderson
description: I am a simple man, who possess good values. I am a very big hearted person who has never lost a child’s ability to unconditionally love. So I am an emotional and romantic soul. I have a lot of respect for women. I think that women possess an inner strength that most guys can not see let alone understand. I am not intimidated nor am I embarrassed by a woman’s intellect or her success.
